Package com.commander4j.db

Class JDBWasteLocation

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.commander4j.db.JDBWasteLocation
  • public class JDBWasteLocation
extends java.lang.Object
    The JDBWasteLocation class updates the table APP_WASTE_LOCATION. This table contains a single row for each unique Waste Location as stored in the APP_WASTE_LOCATION table.

    See Also:
    JDBWasteReasons, JDBWasteReportingIDS, JDBWasteTransactionType, JDBWasteLocationReporting, JDBWasteTypes, JDBWasteMaterial, JDBWasteLog
